Class GazeteerCSVImporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dgfoundation.amp.importers.AmpImporter
      • org.dgfoundation.amp.importers.CSVImporter
        • org.dgfoundation.amp.importers.GazeteerCSVImporter

  • public class GazeteerCSVImporter
extends CSVImporter
    In order to import the file, copy the csv for the country you want to import locations (extracted from http://download.geonames.org/export/dump/) into the directory /doc and save with the name: gazeteer.csv When AMP is started the locations will be imported into the DB
